wiki.content:
Tillana (the fast-paced, rhythmic item usually ending a recital) in Nattai Raga.  This tillana concerns Lord Krishna's battle with the sea serpents. It's normally called Kalinga Mardana Tillana.

track.name: Tillana
comments: Kalinga Mardana Tillana - in Ganberra Natai raga. SO invogorating at any tempo - she sped it up for this one.
